{"tid":1616562,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新手養狗一問","createTime":"2019-10-03T13:02:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T23:32:27.000Z","uid":318714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"297b6bdc6d5dd7e310026fd7d7c143600283f9e5","tid":1616562,"uid":318714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:02:31.000Z","msg":"黎緊打算養貴婦<br />\n養貴婦會唔會有咩要留意<br />\n同埋貴婦多數性格係點"},{"pid":"6fa5f230579d7770db833e03797619ad025f3dd9","tid":1616562,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:38:16.000Z","msg":"好聰明 要勤力啲梳毛<br />\n其實可以買啲書睇睇先<br />\n基本上而家啲書 由你接狗仔前嘅準備功夫<br />\n到點樣教佢 都好詳細"},{"pid":"f011fb1c68719942c82b21b4c7ff2d830a1d23ac","tid":1616562,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"297b6bdc6d5dd7e310026fd7d7c143600283f9e5","tid":1616562,"uid":318714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:02:31.000Z","msg":"黎緊打算養貴婦<br />\n養貴婦會唔會有咩要留意<br />\n同埋貴婦多數性格係點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T18:14:15.000Z","msg":"最重要<br />\n如果由bb養起<br />\n接左返屋企千祈咪畀佢係咁跳係咁快跑<br />\n貴婦狗隻腳真係好撚易斷！手術都成幾皮野<br />\n同埋小心踩到佢！佢好細粒"},{"pid":"51ec73f2eb6b66dfbeb25f51ac098390338f1fb9","tid":1616562,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T18:14:30.000Z","msg":"支持領養"},{"pid":"7c23c726b924358807341943a7814312b9c895b5","tid":1616562,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:07:27.000Z","msg":"你鐘意細狗多D？我有個朋友之前失戀咗幾年，但自從一年前養咗隻狗同隻兔仔之後，愛情運越來越好，之後佢去玩塔羅占卜嗰陣，個占卜師話原來佢兩隻寵物嘅星座旺佢嘅星座，仲講仲咗佢男朋友嘅職業同埋家景富裕，話今年會結婚，結果真係三個星期前結咗婚，仲去埋巴里渡蜜月... 真係而加先知原來養寵物都可以改運，犀利! 我個朋友本身都好鐘意寵物，但知道咗旺佢之後更加錫哂佢地🤣<br />\n<br />\n咁啱我又睇咗呢個video，裡面嗰個係真係專業占星師:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Qf8or0P4aZM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQf8or0P4aZM&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=696fb9d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Qf8or0P4aZM</a><br />\n<br />\n你不防都試下啦😊"},{"pid":"db293f69791f09c083b21e2bdc8726f97bf3f85b","tid":1616562,"uid":335492,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"297b6bdc6d5dd7e310026fd7d7c143600283f9e5","tid":1616562,"uid":318714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:02:31.000Z","msg":"黎緊打算養貴婦<br />\n養貴婦會唔會有咩要留意<br />\n同埋貴婦多數性格係點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:43:42.000Z","msg":"(我養緊poodle)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">poodle真係好聰明</span></span></strong> <br />\n我自己養過兩隻<br />\n同埋去開狗公園<br />\n總結吓比你參考<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">1.佢地好聰明</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">好恰嘅人佢未必聽你話</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">知邊個唔得罪得</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">都易訓練</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">領悟力強 明白你想佢點</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2.佢地演技好</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">好識扮野eg扮可憐</div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我隻狗試過打完針翻到屋企狂叫 嚇到我地即刻帶佢翻診所 結果醫生話：戲精!好小氣喎 扭計姐 冇事</span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">做錯野你打/鬧佢 佢會扮可憐令你心軟</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>一定要盡早開始教</ins></span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">見過有啲人唔教 隻poodle會周圍咬人/狗 狂吠 嗌破喉嚨都唔應主人 完全失控 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有啲人可能會同你講 poodle咁細隻冇力架唔驚佢咬人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我個人認為除左tea cup細力少少(係少少only) poodle 唔細力 而且同狗打交會受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div>"},{"pid":"c63a99774501dfcf592f1b08b066aae0a5ac7d6c","tid":1616562,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:11:57.000Z","msg":"Nowadays dogs certainly don't come cheap."},{"pid":"d2f94fc6f6b3e227ad7eadf495d85b0a616bcb2e","tid":1616562,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:13:22.000Z","msg":"it's expensive to buy everything they need including getting them spayed or neutered."},{"pid":"6291129cf8b6f362ebf3a32d1a6eedbcb43bc4a9","tid":1616562,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:15:47.000Z","msg":"including any medications they need when they have a condition."},{"pid":"46ec77950c3f7edb0fe99458a78e81d28598d51a","tid":1616562,"uid":321544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T23:32:27.000Z","msg":"救吓警犬！<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/stop-hong-kong-police-force-bringing-police-dog-front-line-while-they-are-usingused-chemical-weapons\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fstop-hong-kong-police-force-bringing-police-dog-front-line-while-they-are-usingused-chemical-weapons&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=3df87840\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/stop-hong-kong-police-force-bringing-police-dog-front-line-while-they-are-usingused-chemical-weapons</a>"}]}